ks effortless and might even feel that way at times\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s kind of just relaxing sometimes,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094but winning the 200-meter breaststroke Thursday was hardly soft stuff.\\u00c2 Douglass walked clear-eyed into an alley fight with South African Tatjana Smith, the reigning gold medalist in the event and the winner in the 100 breast earlier this week.\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her long-gliding breaststroke\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"effortless\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"that way\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"times\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200-meter breaststroke\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"hardly soft stuff\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Douglass\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"an alley fight\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"South African Tatjana Smith\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"the reigning gold medalist\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 breast\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She walked away with a victory by .36 seconds, breaking her own American record and giving Team USA a jolt of adrenaline.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999840624958782, \"rank\": 0.00014811467753217305, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States