\"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"a fine accomplishment\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bar has been set extremely high by previous generations.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bar\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"previous generations\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 400 freestyle relay cleared the bar on the first night.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 400 freestyle relay\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"the first night\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Torri Huske surprisingly sailed over it in the 100 butterfly.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Torri Huske\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100 butterfly\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Katie Ledecky soared past it for the eighth time in her legendary career in the 1,500 freestyle.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eighth time\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"her legendary career\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500 freestyle\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that was it.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of close races went the wrong way, and the Greatness Roadblock created by Frenchman L\\u00c3\\u00a9on Marchand, Canadian Summer McIntosh and a whole host of Aussie women kept the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cStar Spangled Banner\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d out of heavy rotation at La D\\u00c3\\u00a9fense Arena.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Amazing_Race\", \"score\": 0.9999999987749106, \"rank\": 1.2250087238620192e-09, \"text\": \"Roadblock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Amazing_Race\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Amazing_Race\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999998793659943, \"rank\": 1.2063297159738245e-07, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Summer McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A number\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"close races\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"Frenchman L\\u00c3\\u00a9\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole host\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"Aussie women\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cStar Spangled Banner\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1658}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy rotation\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"La D\\u00c3\\u00a9fense Arena\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were keeping the cowbell quiet, to the delight of Aussie trash talker Cate Campbell.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cowbell\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"the delight\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"Aussie trash talker Cate Campbell\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Very few of the results were particularly shocking to people who were paying attention before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was always going to be a tough battle against an improving world.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough battle\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"an improving world\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But America\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s inability to hit some of the customary high notes created angst at home.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"America\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s inability\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"the customary high notes\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"angst\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was angst that Douglass and her teammates have tried to tune out.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"