ecord in the 200 breast in January.\\u00c2 USA Swimming put her larger-than-life face on the side of Lucas Oil Stadium for Olympic Trials\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094not Ledecky, not Caeleb Dressel, but the 22-year-old with a single Olympic bronze medal to her name.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2500, \"end\": 2508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999840624958782, \"rank\": 0.00014811467753217305, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"increasing expectations\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"poise\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 breast\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 USA Swimming\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"Lucas Oil Stadium\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Trials\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094not Ledecky\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"a single Olympic bronze medal\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a lot to live up to.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglass handled that with aplomb, winning three events in Indianapolis to back up the billing.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2776, \"end\": 2784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.7046927978748084e-12, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}, {\"begin\": 2835, \"end\": 2847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9979627812392626, \"rank\": 0.001977816958039016, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aplomb\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"the billing\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ultra-versatile Douglass chose to drop the 100 freestyle from her program here\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094in part because she wanted to pour her focus into the 200 breast and 200 individual medley (which starts Friday), plus a full relay load.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 3095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.7046927978748084e-12, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100 freestyle\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2933}, {\"ngram\": \"her program\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"her focus\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 breast\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngra